  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. Intended use is pre-market submission support for a Class II spinal fixation device under 21 CFR 888.3070. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance level.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-compression-bending-claim",
